# 📂 Data

This folder contains the dataset used for building the Customer Churn Prediction model.

## 📊 Dataset Overview
The dataset includes customer demographic details, account information, and service usage patterns. It is used to analyze and predict whether a customer is likely to churn.

## 🔑 Key Features
- Customer demographics (gender, senior citizen, dependents)
- Account details (tenure, contract type)
- Services used (internet, streaming, support)
- Billing information (monthly charges, payment method)
- Target variable: Churn (Yes/No)

## ⚙️ Usage
The dataset is used for:
- Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)
- Feature Engineering
- Model Training

## 🧹 Data Processing
- Handled missing values
- Encoded categorical variables
- Scaled numerical features (if required)

## 📌 Note
This dataset is for educational and project purposes only.
